    "These rules can be broken down into three stages: planning, scheduling, and resource assignment.",
    "These decisions are interdependent and hierarchical and are made over different periods of time [6].",
    "The MS-RCPSP has numerous real-life applications in various industries.",
    "For instance, in software development, MS-RCPSP can help allocate and schedule development tasks across a team of developers who have different skills and availability.",
    "Similarly, in manufacturing, it can be used to schedule production tasks across different machines and workers with different skills."
